# UI/UX and Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS classes consistently with `dark:` variants for dark mode.
- Prefer `react-icons` over inline `<svg>` or ASCII emojis. Use icons from `react-icons/hi2` for consistency.
- Follow layout conventions: rely on shared layout containers for outer padding; avoid redundant per-page padding.
- Maintain consistent alignment across admin/organizer pages. Use wrappers like `max-w-7xl mx-auto` where appropriate.
- Forms and overlays should support keyboard (e.g., ESC to close) and click-outside dismissal when relevant.
- all button delete, change status of booking will require confirmation. using confirmation modal consistently